 Present arguments whether or not a proposed treatment of PD calibration for low-default portfolios is compliant with regulation Give a comprehensive list of potential deficiencies of a downturn LGD derivation based on shared documentation Identify the major policy decisions underlying a compliant EAD estimation for a low-default specialized lending portfolio Compare and understand the impact of different treatments of LGD estimation based on prepared code samples and realistic data sets  Online and offline This course can be organised in an offline, an online, or a combined on- and offline version.
